{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"2":{"eng-name":"The Book of the Prayer","ara-name":"كتاب الصلاة"}},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":667,"hadithnumber_last":705,"arabicnumber_first":667,"arabicnumber_last":705}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":673,"arabicnumber":673,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن بشار، حدثنا يحيى بن سعيد، عن شعبة، عن سماك بن حرب، عن جابر بن سمرة، ان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يصلي الظهر اذا دحضت الشمس","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":7},"chapter":{"id":3,"ara-name":"باب وَقْتِ صَلاَةِ الظُّهْرِ ","eng-name":"The Time Of The Zuhr Prayer","isFirstHadith":true}}]}